# disbursementCardUnsupportedError()

**Type Method**

Creates an error that indicates that the selected payment pass doesn’t support receiving funds through disbursements.

## Declaration

```swift
class func disbursementCardUnsupportedError() -> any Error
```

## Return Value

An [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSError] that describes the error condition.

## Handling errors

- **disbursementContactInvalidError(withContactField:localizedDescription:)**: Creates a recipient contact error with the supplied field.
